description: Sanitarium So Good No Added Sugar Oat Milk is a long life dairy free milk made from Australian oats.So Good™ No Added Sugar Oat Milk is a dairy free milk made with the goodness of oats. Our Australian grown oats are softly milled and blended with the best ingredients to create an oat milk that is totally creamy in taste.  So Good™ Oat Milk No Added Sugar can be used in any of the ways that you would normally use dairy milk. Its creamy taste and natural sweetness make it the perfect addition to your favourite cereal or smoothie. It can also be used in hot drinks and cooking, or enjoyed ice cold by the glass.Australian Grown OatsDairy and Lactose FreeNo Added SugarHigh in CalciumSource of Vitamins B2, B12 and D
